The paper discusses a channel simulation software for 5G wireless communications, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), systems and control (cs.SY), and augmented reality (cs.AR). However, since the focus is on channel modeling and simulation, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
